00:25:35,260 --> 00:25:36,800
Murakami-san...

367
00:25:37,220 --> 00:25:38,430
Murakami-san...

368
00:25:38,970 --> 00:25:40,180
Murakami-san...

369
00:25:40,600 --> 00:25:41,890
Murakami-san...

370
00:25:42,470 --> 00:25:45,480
Vestir-se!  O tempo está
prestes a começar de novo...

371
00:25:49,150 --> 00:25:53,530
Murakami-san parecia
um tanto desapontado.

372
00:25:53,530 --> 00:25:57,530
Como se... ela
quisesse ser descoberta.

373
00:25:58,490 --> 00:26:00,870
Faremos o mesmo amanhã?

374
00:26:01,580 --> 00:26:02,910
Murakami-san...

375
00:26:03,330 --> 00:26:04,500
Murakami-san...

376
00:26:10,130 --> 00:26:11,040
Moritani-san!

377
00:26:11,040 --> 00:26:13,050
Huh?  Murakami-san!!

378
00:26:13,590 --> 00:26:15,420
